name: With Open Wings
description:
Beat your time by gliding through feather hoops and reaching the end of the race as fast as possible.

Master the bird's wing to dive, swoop, flap and glide your way to the top!
This being a jam game, you have no one else to compare yourself too other than yourself.
What times can you score on the 9 default levels?

Don't think you have enough?
You can create more levels using Tiled.
